Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:23.58,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,We will be staying at the front for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らは\Nしばらく この前線に とどまる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この先\N武功は上げられぬと覚悟しておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:26.90,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Be prepared to not render any more achievements.
